text: Kao Hao-wen (; born 17 March 1995 in Hualien City) is a male Chinese Taipei recurve archer. He competed in the archery competition at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Taiwanese male archers Category:Living people Category:1995 births Category:Archers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic archers of Taiwan
